videos.headline: Cougars strike first with 1-yard TD run
videos.description: James Williams gets behind his blockers and powers across the goal line, giving Washington State an early 7-0 lead over Arizona.

videos.headline: Strong shows incredible concentration on INT
videos.description: Marcus Strong intercepts Khalil Tate while falling to the ground, setting up another Washington State touchdown drive.

videos.headline: Borghi doubles Cougars' lead with 1-yard TD
videos.description: Max Borghi takes the handoff and wills his way across the goal line to capitalize on the Wildcats' turnover and make it 14-0.

videos.headline: Arizona slices lead in half with 24-yard TD pass
videos.description: Khalil Tate puts one up for Shawn Poindexter, who makes the adjustment and hauls it in as he falls to the ground to make it 14-7 Cougars.

videos.headline: Minshew finds Jackson for 27-yard catch-and-run
videos.description: Gardner Minshew throws a strike to Calvin Jackson Jr., who weaves his way to the end zone to extend the Cougars' lead to 21-7.

videos.headline: Minshew throws 11-yard TD strike
videos.description: Gardner Minshew throws on target to Dezmon Patmon, who absorbs a hit and holds on to make it 28-7 Cougars.

videos.headline: Tate airs it out for 37-yard TD
videos.description: Khalil Tate rolls to his right and throws downfield to Tony Ellison, who gets a step and crosses the goal line to cut the Cougars' lead to 28-14.

videos.headline: Minshew throws 3rd TD pass of half
videos.description: Gardner Minshew throws a dart to Calvin Jackson Jr. on a slant route for a 6-yard touchdown pass to make it 34-14.

videos.headline: Cougars recover own kickoff for bizarre TD
videos.description: Jack Crane kicks it off to Arizona, but it skips past returner Cedric Peterson and bounces all the way to the end zone, where it's recovered for a touchdown by Kainoa Wilson.

videos.headline: Cougars pour it on with 9-yard TD pass
videos.description: Gardner Minshew swings it out to James Williams, who finds space and walks into the end zone to make it 48-14 Washington State.

videos.headline: Wildcats fumble at the 1-inch line
videos.description: Gary Brightwell loses the football as he tries to fight across the goal line, and it gets picked up in the end zone by Marcus Strong to give possession back to the Cougars.

videos.headline: Cougars put up 55 in first half on Minshew's 50-yard TD pass
videos.description: Gardner Minshew lets it fly and connects with Davontavean Martin, who gets all the way down the sideline to make it 55-14 before the break.

videos.headline: Cougars recover fumble on punt return
videos.description: Shun Brown tries to make a play on the punt return, but he coughs it up, and Jahad Woods recovers to give Washington State great field position.

videos.headline: Minshew ties school record with 6th TD pass of game
videos.description: Gardner Minshew rips a pass to Jamire Calvin, who makes the grab in the end zone and extends the Cougars' lead to 62-28 early in the 4th quarter.

videos.headline: Minshew's 7th TD pass sets new school record
videos.description: Gardner Minshew throws on target to Calvin Jackson Jr., who makes the catch in the end zone to give Minshew his 7th touchdown pass of the game.
